import React, { Component, Fragment } from 'react'
import MainContainer1 from './mainContainer1'
import MainContainer2 from './mainContainer2'
import MainContainer3 from './mainContainer3'
import Comp1 from './components/Comp1'

import img5 from './images/pic5.jpg'
import img6 from './images/pic6.jpg'
import img7 from './images/pic7.jpg'
import img8 from './images/pic8.jpg'
import img9 from './images/pic9.jpg'
import img10 from './images/pic10.jpg'
import img11 from './images/pic11.jpg'
import img12 from './images/pic12.jpg'
import img13 from './images/pic13.jpg'
import img14 from './images/pic14.jpg'
import img15 from './images/pic15.jpg'
import img16 from './images/pic16.jpg'
import img17 from './images/pic17.jpg'

import './postButtonCSS.css'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom'


const arr = [
    {   img: img5,
        feature: 'featured',
        title: 'devSpartan'
    },
    {   img: img6,
        feature: 'simple',
        title: 'devSpartan2'
    },
    {   img: img7,
        feature: 'fashion',
        title: 'devSpartan'
    },
    {   img: img8,
        feature: 'featured',
        title: 'devSpartan2'
    },
    {   img: img9,
        feature: 'day',
        title: 'devSpartan'
    },
    {   img: img10,
        feature: 'fasion',
        title: 'devSpartan2'
    },
    {   img: img11,
        feature: 'simple',
        title: 'get together in fun way'
    },
    {   img: img12,
        feature: 'featured',
        title: 'easer day outfit ideas'
    },
    {   img: img13,
        feature: 'fashion',
        title: 'devSpartan'
    },
    {   img: img14,
        feature: 'day',
        title: 'festival favourite look'
    },
    {   img: img15,
        feature: 'featured',
        title: 'things you should try'
    },
    {   img: img16,
        feature: 'simple',
        title: 'new look for new year'
    }
]

class ActionComponent extends Component {

    render() {
        return (
            <Router>
                <Fragment>
                    <Route path='/' exact strict component={MainContainer1} />
                    <Route path='/page2' exact component={MainContainer2} />
                    <Route path='/page3' exact component={MainContainer3} />
                    <Route path='/postpage' exact render={() => {
                        return(
                            <Comp1 data={arr}/>
                        )
                    }} />
                    
                </Fragment>
            </Router>
        )
    }
}

export default ActionComponent
